    <!-- Inspiration Section -->
    <section class="inspiration-section" id="inspiration">
        <div class="cta-box">
            <span class="nav-arrow-down" onclick="smartScrollToSection('#what-is-sorana')">⬇️</span>
            <span class="nav-arrow-up" onclick="window.scrollTo({top: 0, behavior: 'smooth'})">⬆️</span>
            <h2>Inspiration</h2>
            <p>We were frustrated by the limitations of traditional file managers. For decades, we've been forced to organize digital lives into rigid, list-based hierarchies and nested folders that hide information rather than reveal it. Our brains don't work in lists; they work through associations and spatial relationships. We wanted to build a system that reflects this—moving away from "where did I save that file?" to "what is this project about?" by using semantic and visual grouping to reveal the hidden structure of our data.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="intro-section" id="what-is-sorana">
        <h2>What is Sorana?</h2>
        <div class="cta-box">
            <span class="nav-arrow-down" onclick="smartScrollToSection('#core-capabilities')">⬇️</span>
            <span class="nav-arrow-up" onclick="smartScrollToSection('#inspiration')">⬆️</span>
            <p>Sorana is an AI-powered visual workspace featuring a built-in MCP server for file operations, web content tools, OCR document processing, and spatial AI organization. Transform how you organize digital files with semantic analysis that groups related content onto an intuitive 2D canvas. Create no-code agent workflows, enhance document context with OCR, perform file and web operations through the MCP server, and connect to on-prem or cloud AI backends (OpenAI, Mistral, Google Gemini, 🍋 Lemonade with FastFlowLM NPU, and more) while keeping your data under your control. With advanced 4-tier AI memory and 40x faster RAG retrieval, Sorana delivers intelligent, context-aware responses while saving tokens.</p>
        </div>

