        <section class="capabilities-section" id="core-capabilities">
            <h2>Core Capabilities</h2>
            <div class="cta-box">
                <span class="nav-arrow-down" onclick="smartScrollToSection('#intended-users')">⬇️</span>
                <span class="nav-arrow-up" onclick="smartScrollToSection('#what-is-sorana')">⬆️</span>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Spatial AI Organization:</strong> Uses AI to semantically group files and arrange them on a 2D canvas, providing a visual overview of projects.</li>
                    <li><strong>WYSIWYG Canvas Editor:</strong> Direct manipulation of workspace elements. Drag and drop files between groups, create new categories, rename items, and adjust group boundaries.</li>
                    <li><strong>Advanced Model Management & AI Integration:</strong> Connect to multiple cloud and on-prem LLM backends including OpenAI, Mistral, Google Gemini, 🍋 Lemonade, Ollama, Llama.Cpp, and other compatible services. The model manager lists all available models and allows users to activate or deactivate models as needed for specific tasks. Supports seamless connection to both on-prem and cloud-based AI services.</li>
        <li><strong>No-Code Multi-Agent Orchestration:</strong> Create custom agents and connect them into processing pipelines using a drag-and-drop interface within our unique 2D canvas workspace where files and folders are spatially arranged. Handle complex multi-agent workflows by building agents that operate directly on this visual workspace, collaborating seamlessly by passing insights from one to another to solve complex problems, all without writing code. Enhance agent knowledge by integrating OCR-processed PDFs and text files directly into their memory and processing capabilities.</li>

        <figure class="chatbot-figure">
            <img src="chatbot.png" alt="Sorana No-Code Multi-Agent Orchestration Interface" class="chatbot-screenshot">
        </figure>

        <li><strong>Visual Structure Mapping:</strong> Generate dynamic visual representations and mind maps of folder hierarchies to understand relationships and reveal the big picture of your data organization.</li>
        <li><strong>Built-in MCP Server <span class="beta-feature">beta</span>:</strong> Integrated server supporting advanced file operations and web content access through AI agents:
            <ul>
                <li><strong>File Operations:</strong> read_file, read_file_from_line, write_file, list_directory, create_directory, move_file, search_files, get_file_info, edit_file, get_filesystem_info</li>
                <li><strong>Web Content Tools:</strong> web_fetch_content, web_scrape_page, web_extract_links, web_search, web_get_metadata, web_save_snapshot</li>
            </ul>
            Combine file and web operations for powerful workflows (e.g., "Fetch product specs from website and save to local file").
        </li>
        <li><strong>Chat History & Conversation Management:</strong> All your past conversations are stored in a sidebar. Search, reload, and delete chats. Nothing gets lost.</li>
        <li><strong>4-Tier AI Memory System:</strong> Advanced memory architecture with short-term memory, conversation summaries, long-term memory (personas, facts, preferences), and document search. Each layer builds on the last for intelligent, context-aware responses.</li>
        <li><strong>40x Faster RAG Retrieval:</strong> Optimized startup from 4s to under 0.1s. Token-efficient, targeted answers with full user control over stored data.</li>
        <li><strong>Google Gemini Support:</strong> Add your API key and use Gemini models including free tier options.</li>
        <li><strong>NPU-Aware Document Search:</strong> Uses 🍋 Lemonade backend with integrated FastFlowLM NPU for Windows Ryzen. 🍋 Lemonade is AMD's new high-performance AI server (C++ based) that integrates multiple backends including Llama.cpp, Whisper, and FastFlowLM for NPU acceleration. Falls back to text-based retrieval if no NPU is available. Supports 15 languages with auto-detection.</li>
        <li><strong>Centralized Data Storage:</strong> All data stored in a single <code>.sorana/</code> folder. Existing installs migrate automatically.</li>
        <li><strong>Portable:</strong> The application is portable and keeps data under user control.</li>
    </ul>
    </div>

